sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ Reencrypt
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>SubjectAccessReview
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>TLS (service-ca)
    participant S3 as Object Store (S3)<br/>443/9000 TCP<br/>TLS (configurable)
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pods as Pipeline Pods
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (service-ca)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,PA: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (Reencrypt TLS)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>datasciencepipelinesapplications/api
    KRBP->>API: Forward (verified)<br/>8888/TCP HTTPS (service-ca)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AccessKey/SecretKey
    API->>Argo: Create Workflow CR<br/>K8s API 443/TCP TLS 1.2+

    Note over Argo,Pods: Pipeline DAG Execution

    Argo->>Pods: Create pipeline step pods<br/>K8s API ServiceAccount Token
    Pods->>MLMD: Log metadata/artifacts<br/>8080/TCP gRPC TLS (service-ca)
    MLMD->>DB: Persist metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS
    Pods->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over PA,API: Status Synchronization

    PA->>API: Sync run status<br/>8888/TCP HTTPS (internal)
    API->>DB: Update run status<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: MLMD Metadata Access

    User->>Route: gRPC metadata request<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (Reencrypt TLS)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview
    Note right of KRBP: MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP localhost
    KRBP->>MLMD: Forward via Envoy<br/>8080/TCP gRPC TLS
    MLMD->>DB: Query metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: Metadata results
    MLMD-->>User: gRPC Response

    Note over User,PA: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation

    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    DSPO->>K8s: Watch DSPA CRs<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+ SA Token
    K8s-->>DSPO: DSPA CR event
    DSPO->>DB: Health check<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS
    DSPO->>S3: Health check<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    DSPO->>K8s: Create/Update deployments<br/>Services, Routes, NetworkPolicies
